<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to RBC EduHub</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f7f7fa; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 480px; margin: 32px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #0001; padding: 32px; }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .logo { height: 40px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .success { font-size: 1.3em; color: #008a3d; margin: 24px 0; text-align: center; }
    .footer { font-size: 0.95em; color: #888; text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="../images/rbclogo.png" alt="RBC EduHub" class="logo" />
      <h2>Welcome to RBC EduHub!</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Hello{{#if name}}, {{name}}{{/if}},</p>
    <div class="success">
      Your account was created successfully as a <strong>{{roleName}}</strong>!<br>
      You can now log in and start using all the features of RBC EduHub.
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      If you have any questions, reply to this email.<br>
      &copy; {{year}} RBC EduHub
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
